      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/china-slashes-steel-output-as-industry-sounds-alarm-on-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于需求低迷，利润率大幅下降，中国钢铁制造商上个月大幅削减产量。]]></description>
